{"tid":2250700,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"Pantry雪櫃當私家雪櫃班撚樣","createTime":"2020-10-20T09:37:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T03:39:40.000Z","uid":351252,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"25c374ede8904550ac7aeed3e688df1542632b00","tid":2250700,"uid":351252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T09:37:58.000Z","msg":"有班撚樣將pantry雪櫃當自己屋企雪櫃<br />\n買一堆菜呀肉呀汽水雪糕乜鳩就擺入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同事擺飯盒就冇位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老味最誇張係有個櫃係俾呢班撚樣放自己啲碗碟同煲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有次仲好撚得戚咁同人講個櫃係專for佢哋<br />\n洗個手都抆兩三張廚房紙<br />\n洗完飯盒又幾張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你明明有乾淨毛巾可以用<br />\n唔洗你錢買廚房紙都唔洗咁呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我心諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如將個pantry俾你班撚樣專用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最撚正係佢哋帶私家煲返嚟煮菜就得<br />\n其他同事用pantry本身有嘅煲蒸嘢就話唔好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜撚"},{"pid":"b62534c1b1b702fdbbc8979fbcfb86da0a3af5f0","tid":2250700,"uid":254452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T09:51:10.000Z","msg":"你係咪我同事 同我嗰度班人情況一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db21f8ae87039553ebf2194ae2f7cce7fa05bae1","tid":2250700,"uid":27416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10